1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,200
13.
No light.

2
00:00:01,250 --> 00:00:03,500
No door.
No sign.

3
00:00:03,550 --> 00:00:06,500
Same face.
New line.

4
00:00:06,550 --> 00:00:09,500
Still quiet.
Still mine.

5
00:00:09,550 --> 00:00:13,000
Out to eat
I used to hide

6
00:00:13,050 --> 00:00:16,500
behind the menu,
behind the glass.

7
00:00:16,550 --> 00:00:20,000
My turn comes.
I look up fast.

8
00:00:20,050 --> 00:00:22,500
"Spicy rigatoni."

9
00:00:22,550 --> 00:00:25,500
That's it.
I asked.

10
00:00:25,550 --> 00:00:28,500
13.
Small jump.

11
00:00:28,550 --> 00:00:31,500
Not brave.
Just enough.

12
00:00:31,550 --> 00:00:34,500
Still weird.
Still me.

13
00:00:34,550 --> 00:00:38,500
Less scared
to be seen.

14
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:43,000
Grocery store.
Leave the cart.

15
00:00:43,050 --> 00:00:46,500
One aisle over.
Beating heart.

16
00:00:46,550 --> 00:00:50,000
Grab the thing.
Walk back smart.

17
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:53,500
No one knows.
I do.

18
00:00:53,550 --> 00:00:56,500
That's the part.

19
00:00:57,500 --> 00:01:00,500
13.
Small jump.

20
00:01:00,550 --> 00:01:03,500
Not brave.
Just enough.

21
00:01:03,550 --> 00:01:06,500
Still weird.
Still me.

22
00:01:06,550 --> 00:01:10,500
Less scared
to be seen.

23
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:15,000
Teacher asks.
No one speaks.

24
00:01:15,050 --> 00:01:18,500
Hints keep coming.
Room feels weak.

25
00:01:18,550 --> 00:01:22,000
I know it.
Raise my hand.

26
00:01:22,050 --> 00:01:26,000
Say the thing.
Room can breathe again.

27
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:31,000
Tomato sauce.
Tomato paste.

28
00:01:31,050 --> 00:01:34,500
Cream in the pan.
Nothing to waste.

29
00:01:34,550 --> 00:01:38,000
No seasoning.
No disguise.

30
00:01:38,050 --> 00:01:42,000
I know enough
when I decide.

31
00:01:43,500 --> 00:01:46,500
13.
Small jump.

32
00:01:46,550 --> 00:01:49,500
Not brave.
Just enough.

33
00:01:49,550 --> 00:01:53,000
I order.
I answer.

34
00:01:53,050 --> 00:01:56,500
I leave.
I come back.

35
00:01:56,550 --> 00:02:00,000
Still weird.
Still me.

36
00:02:00,050 --> 00:02:04,500
Less hidden.
Less scared.
